First Brazilian In Space
Lt. Col. Marcos Pontes, the first Brazilian astronaut, is due to return
from his brief mission tomorrow. What do you think?
Young Woman
Natasha Nicholls,
Hair Stylist
"I'm all for a Brazilian being sent into space, but that spacesuit left
little to the imagination."
Asian Man
Harold Ledin,
Systems Analyst
"I understand this is part of their greater plan to have a lunar favela
by 2028."
Young Man
Darrick Unger,
Botanist
"I wonder how they decided who got to escape Brazil."
